---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const DEALER_EMAIL = "info@alfursanauto.ca";
const EFFECTIVE_DATE = "April 25, 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Alfursan Auto"
  description="How Alfursan Auto collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you apply for vehicle financing."
>
  <main class="pp-wrap">
    <article class="pp-body">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="pp-meta">Effective date: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</p>

      <p>
        Alfursan Auto ("<strong>we</strong>", "<strong>us</strong>", or
        "<strong>our</strong>") is committed to protecting your personal
        information in accordance with Canada's <em>Personal Information
        Protection and Electronic Documents Act</em> (PIPEDA) and applicable
        provincial privacy legislation.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        When you submit a financing application through our website, we collect
        the following categories of personal information:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Identity:</strong> Full name, date of birth, marital status</li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> Phone number, email address</li>
        <li><strong>Residence:</strong> Current and previous addresses, postal codes, duration of residence</li>
        <li><strong>Employment:</strong> Employer name, job title, annual income, employment history</li>
        <li><strong>Vehicle &amp; Loan:</strong> VIN of the vehicle of interest, down payment, preferred loan term</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Government ID (optional):</strong> Photographs of the front and
          back of your driver's licence, uploaded voluntarily to speed up processing
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Supporting financial documents (Phase 2, if requested):</strong>
          void cheque, proof of insurance, and a recent pay stub
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Personal references (Phase 2, if requested):</strong>
          names, phone numbers, and relationships of up to two personal references
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Technical:</strong> A one-way SHA-256 hash of your IP address
          (raw IP is never stored)
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Purpose of Collection</h2>
      <p>We collect this information solely to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Evaluate your eligibility for vehicle financing</li>
        <li>Submit your application to lending partners (with your explicit consent)</li>
        <li>Contact you regarding the status of your application</li>
        <li>Comply with applicable legal and regulatory obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>
        Your information is used only for the purposes described above. We do
        not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to any third party.
        Information is shared with lending institutions <strong>only after you
        have given explicit consent</strong> (Dealertrack consent checkbox in
        your application).
      </p>

      <h2>4. Storage &amp; Security</h2>
      <p>
        All application data is stored in an encrypted database hosted on
        Supabase (servers located in Canada or the United States). Driver's
        licence images are stored in a private, encrypted storage bucket with
        no public access — they are accessible only to authorised dealership
        staff via time-limited signed URLs. We apply reasonable technical and
        organizational safeguards to protect your data against unauthorized
        access, disclosure, or loss.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain financing application records for <strong>seven (7) years</strong>
        from the date of submission, in compliance with PIPEDA and applicable
        financial record-keeping requirements. After this period, records are
        permanently deleted. Driver's licence images are deleted when the
        associated application is removed.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your information (subject to legal retention obligations)</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for the use of your information for financing purposes</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at{" "}
        <a href={`mailto:${DEALER_EMAIL}`}>{DEALER_EMAIL}</a>. We will respond
        within 30 days.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. The effective date at the
        top of this page will reflect the most recent revision. Continued use
        of our website following a material change constitutes acceptance of
        the updated policy.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions or concerns about this policy or our privacy practices may
        be directed to:
      </p>
      <address>
        <strong>Alfursan Auto</strong><br />
        Toronto, Ontario, Canada<br />
        <a href={`mailto:${DEALER_EMAIL}`}>{DEALER_EMAIL}</a>
      </address>
      <p>
        If you are not satisfied with our response, you may file a complaint with
        the <a href="https://www.priv.gc.ca/en/report-a-concern/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Office of the Privacy Commissioner of Canada
        </a>.
      </p>
    </article>

    <p class="pp-back">
      <a href="/finance/">&larr; Back to Financing Application</a>
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .pp-wrap {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
  }

  .pp-body h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: #222732;
  }

  .pp-meta {
    color: #99a1b2;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .pp-body h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #222732;
  }

  .pp-body p,
  .pp-body li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #3a3f4a;
  }

  .pp-body ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin: 8px 0 12px;
  }

  .pp-body li {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .pp-body a {
    color: #B92111;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  address {
    font-style: normal;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #3a3f4a;
  }

  .pp-back {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e4e7ec;
  }

  .pp-back a {
    color: #B92111;
    font-size: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .pp-back a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  code {
    font-size: 13px;
    background: #f4f5f7;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: #222732;
  }
</style>
